0.2.name: wordpress/shootq-wordpress-contact-form-7-integration
0.2.description:
This plugin adds ShootQ integration to all Contact Form 7 forms on your blog.

It does this automatically, by looking at the names of the fields and matching them up with those in the ShootQ API.

This development is thanks to Lizzy C Photography.
